Parse Categorical Output

Source: R/utilityFunctions.R
parseCatOutput.Rd

Helper function for parsing output with variables and categories.

Usage

parseCatOutput(text)

Arguments

text

The output to parse.

Value

The parsed output

Author

Michael Hallquist
